Software projects for Agenda VR3, first Linux PDA
=================================================

This repository contains some of my old personal software projects for
the Agenda VR3 Linux PDA by Agenda Computing, Inc. Agenda VR3 was the
first Linux PDA (Personal Digital Assistant) [1].

[1] https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agenda_VR3

See directory "www" for a copy of the old web site including instructions
and screenshots as well as pre-compiled binaries for Agenda VR3.


